translation[13]{c,v,t}:
  18,98,Kaha yeh sab meray rab ki meharbani hai haan jab meray rab ka wada aayega to issay zamin boss ker dey ga be-shak meray rab ka wada sacha aur haq hai
  18,99,Uss din hum enhen aapas mein aik doosray mein gudd madd hotay huye chor den gay aur soor phoonk diya jayega pus sab ko ikhatha ker kay hum jama ker len gay
  18,100,Uss din hum jahannum ko (bhi) kafiron kay samney laa khara keren gay
  18,101,Jin ki aankhen meri yaad say pardey mein thi aur (amar haq) sunn bhi nahi saktay thay
  18,102,Kiya kafir yeh khayal kiye bethay hain? Kay meray siwa woh meray bandon ko apna himayati bana len gay? (Suno) hum ney to inn kuffaar ki mehmani kay liye jahannum ko tayyar ker rakha hai
  18,103,Keh dijiye kay agar (tum kaho to) mein tumhen bata doon kay ba-aetbaar aemaal sab say ziyada khasaray mein kaun hain
  18,104,Woh hain kay jinki dunyawi zindagi ki tamam tar kosishen bekar hogaeen aur woh issi gumaan mein rahey kay woh boht achay kaam ker rahey hain
  18,105,Yehi woh log hain jinhon ney apney perwerdigar ki aayaton aur uss ki mulaqat say kufur kiya iss liye unn kay aemaal ghaarat hogaye pus qayamat kay din hum unn ka koi wazan qaeem na keren gay
  18,106,Haal yeh hai kay inn ka badla jahannum hai kiyon kay enhon nay kufur kiya aur meri aayaton aur meray rasoolon ko mazaq mein uaraya
  18,107,Jo log eman laye aur unhon ney kaam bhi achay kiye yaqeenan unn kay liye al-firdous kay baaghaat ki mehmani hai
  18,108,Jahan woh humesha raha keren gay jiss jagah ko badalney ka kabhi bhi unn ka irada hi na hoga
  18,109,Keh dijiye kay agar meray perwerdigar ki baton kay likhney kay liye samandar sihaee bann jayen to woh bhi meray rab ki baton kay khatam honey say pehlay hi khatam hojaye ga go hum issi jaisa aur bhi iss ki madad ko ley aayen
  18,110,Aap keh dijiye kay mein to tum jaisa hi aik insan hun. (haan) meri janib wahee ki jati hai kay sab ka mabood aik hi mabood hai to jisay bhi apney perwerdigar say milney ki aarzoo ho ussay chahaye kay nek aemaal keray aur apney perwerdigar ki ibadat mein kissi ko bhi shareeq na keray